        <title>有种一语惊醒梦中人的宿命感</title>
        <link>http://ranch007.github.io/p/%E6%9C%89%E7%A7%8D%E4%B8%80%E8%AF%AD%E6%83%8A%E9%86%92%E6%A2%A6%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%BF%E5%91%BD%E6%84%9F/</link>
